### Local Testing for NFL Analyst Agent
### Run with: func start
### Base URL: http://localhost:7071

@baseUrl = http://localhost:7071

### ============================================
### ENDPOINTS
### ============================================

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### Auth Status - Check if GITHUB_TOKEN is configured
GET {{baseUrl}}/agent/auth-status

### Chat - Ask about the Super Bowl
POST {{baseUrl}}/agent/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "prompt": "Who is playing in the Super Bowl this year?"
}

### Chat - Team comparison
POST {{baseUrl}}/agent/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "prompt": "Compare the Chiefs and Eagles head to head"
}

### Chat - Prediction
POST {{baseUrl}}/agent/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "prompt": "Who do you think wins the Super Bowl and why?"
}

### Chat - Stats deep dive
POST {{baseUrl}}/agent/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "prompt": "Show me the current NFL standings"
}

### Chat - How is this built?
POST {{baseUrl}}/agent/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "prompt": "How are you deployed? What Azure services power this agent?"
}
